Features:
Multiple Lists: Create separate lists for different purposes, such as "Work," "Personal," "Shopping," and more.
Recurring Tasks: Set recurring tasks to automatically reappear after a specified interval (daily, weekly, monthly).
Tags and Priorities: Tag tasks for easy filtering (e.g., "Urgent," "Important") and set priority levels to organize tasks by importance.
Due Dates and Reminders: Assign due dates and set reminders to receive alerts as deadlines approach.
Calendar View: Display tasks on a calendar to visually organize your week/month.
Search and Filter: Quickly search tasks or filter by tags, priority, or due dates.
Dark Mode and Themes: Switch between dark mode, light mode, or custom themes.
Progress Tracking: Visualize completed tasks with a progress bar.
Notes Section: Add detailed notes to each task for additional context.
